      "amount": "1/4 tsp",
      "notes": "fine"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350°F (180°C).",
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine the flaked almonds, honey, cinnamon, cayenne pepper, ghee, cardamom, and salt. Mix well until the almonds are evenly coated.",
    "Add the melted coconut oil to the bowl and mix until the almonds are well coated.",
    "Transfer the almond mixture to a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Bake for 15-20 minutes, or until the almonds are lightly toasted and fragrant.",
    "Remove the baking sheet from the oven and let it cool completely.",
    "Once the bake has cooled, break it into pieces and serve."
  ],
